{"timestamp": "2025-12-05 13:25:44.223394", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission recorded.\n\nSummary of submission:\n- is_anomaly: false\n- faulty_devices: []\n- root_cause_name: []\n\nRationale:\n- Diagnosis report found OSPF stable, routing correct, targeted ICMP tests to DNS succeeded, and services (BIND and Apache) listening. Many broad-scan entries were \"unknown\" due to limited coverage, but that is an instrumentation limitation rather than confirmed failures. No device or configuration was identified as faulty; therefore no anomaly was reported.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2517, "output_tokens": 102, "total_tokens": 2619, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1664}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
